Fill in PORT variable in .env file or it will run on port 3000 



GET request example
    Gets all the users
        http://localhost:3000/api/users/   
    
    Gets user by id 1
        http://localhost:3000/api/users/id/1   

    Gets user by name Gohar
        http://localhost:3000/api/users/name/Gohar


POST request

    Expects JSON object
    Creates new user and returns all users
        http://localhost:3000/api/users/  

PUT request
    Expects JSON object
    Updates user by id 1 and returns updated user
        http://localhost:3000/api/users/id/1

DELETE request        
   Deletes user by id 1 and returns all users
        http://localhost:3000/api/users/id/1
